data.description: Just WOW!! Remarkable, energy-efficient home in Sierra Montana awaits you! Offering 6 beds, 3.5 baths, RV gate, and a 3-car garage w/extended driveway. Be greeted by a welcoming living adorned with a high vaulted ceiling that makes a grand impression!  Continue onto the family room that opens to the kitchen, featuring a fireplace and built-in entertainment. You'll love the gourmet kitchen, boasting granite counters, recessed lighting, a pantry, staggered cabinetry, a wine rack, an island w/breakfast bar, and SS appliances w/cooktop gas & double-ovens. Its unique attribute is the stone arch that frames the SS range hood! First floor features a guest quarters, with 2 adjoining rooms & a  private bathroom. Backyard is a true oasis with gorgeous POOL, grass area & area ready for hot tub too! Moving upstairs, the large loft provides a flexible space ideal for a play or TV area. The oversized main bedroom has a double-door entry & fireplace as well! Its ensuite includes dual sinks, separate tub/shower, & a walk-in closet. Laundry room with sink & cabinetry for convenience and more storage. PLUS! This gem has pre-wired surround sound for the ultimate audio experience. You'll love the spacious backyard, a haven of relaxation and entertainment! With its covered patio, built-in BBQ, hot tub pad, and sparkling pool, this space promises year-round enjoyment. Don't miss it!
